column2: SELECT   p.objID, p.parentID, p.specObjID, p.ra, p.dec,   p.modelMag_u, p.modelMag_g, p.modelMag_r, p.modelMag_i, p.modelMag_z,  p.modelMagErr_u, p.modelMagErr_g, p.modelMagErr_r, p.modelMagErr_i, p.modelMagErr_z,  p.flags,  lnLExp_r,LnLDev_r,  dbo.fPhotoTypeN(p.type) as type,  p.fracDev_r,p.expAB_r,p.expRad_r,(p.modelMag_r+#*log(p.expRad_r)) FROM PhotoObj p  WHERE   p.ra > #. AND p.ra < #.  AND p.dec > #. AND p.dec < #.  AND (p.modelMag_r+#*log(p.expRad_r)) > #  AND p.modelMag_r > # AND p.modelMag_r < #.  AND p.expAB_r < #  AND p.expRad_r > #  AND (p.modelMag_g - p.modelMag_i) < #.   AND (p.modelMag_g - p.modelMag_i) > #.  AND p.fracDev_r < #  ORDER BY p.ra
